_json.description: I worked on the sun room today - check out my stories and see if I used shiplap or not🤷🏻‍♀️. It is coming along and I am seriously so happy with it. I can’t wait to have it put together! Furniture arrives tomorrow (insert happy dance 💃🏻). That means I’ll be working into the night.💪🏼 I’m taking this opportunity (while my house is a total disaster) to share some beautiful and inspiring accounts with you all.
